main event: A civilian reported an unusual light in the sky, observed for 30 minutes on July 25, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as looking like a star and moving at a slower pace than two aircraft nearby,The sighting took place at night and was visually observed from the ground,The object eventually faded from sight while continuing in a straight line course, No physical evidence or photographs were available to support the sighting, The conclusion was that it was likely a high flying aircraft or satellite.
sighted object: an unusual light in the sky
location: 12 miles NE of Bruf1, Texas, USA
witness description: Civilian, aged 23, reliable source according to the preparing officer.
